{{Dialogue Start}}
:<!--Trigger PerformanceE 504111001: Config/Level/Mission/5041110/Act/Act504111001.json-->
:'''Audata:''' Oh? You're a friend of Phainon? Welcome, welcome! Sorry, I just came in from the fields and got a bit of messy...
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Have you been busy with the fields?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504111003-->
::'''Audata:''' Hehe, not too bad. The Month of Cultivation and Month of Reaping are the toughest, but the rest of the time's pretty manageable.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Hard work's a kind of joy, isn't it?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504111005-->
::'''Audata:''' Hehe, it surely is. Seeing the wheat grow tall and golden... it just makes me smile, you know?
:<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_504111006-->
:<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504111006-->
:'''Audata:''' Ah! Look at me &mdash; got so caught up chatting I forgot my manners!
:'''Audata:''' Come on in, make yourself at home. Once my kid's back, I'll have you all try my best honey suncake, and the smoked meat I just finished curing!
:<!--Ends the current performance-->
{{Dialogue End}}
